Create a mini e-commerce website using HTML, CSS and JavaScript.  
Display products dynamically with add-to-cart functionality.  
Build a cart page showing selected items, quantity and total price.  
Add a checkout page for order confirmation.  
Create a Node.js backend using Express.  
When an order is placed, save user details, products and total price into a local text file.  
Keep UI modern, logic simple and code beginner friendly.
